      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下Atlas的组织结构关系。最顶层是Organization，一个组织下面可以有很多Projects，这个关系是一对多的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "has many"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Organization到Projects是一对多。那Projects这边呢？每个Project是不是只属于一个Organization？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，一个Project只能属于一个Organization，所以是严格的一对多关系，用双竖线到花括号那种。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Organization和Projects的关系我先画好了。接下来还有什么实体？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-ORGANIZATION",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "has many"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Projects下面还要挂两个东西：MongoDB的Clusters，还有Teams。都是一个Project可以有很多Clusters，也可以有很多Teams。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS",
        "has many"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Clusters和Teams之间有关系吗？还是都只跟Projects关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS",
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前只跟Projects关联，Clusters和Teams之间没有直接关系。都是Projects一对多指向它们。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ATLAS-PROJECTS",
        "MONGODB-CLUSTERS",
        "ATLAS-TEAMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
